          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有一个匝数为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">匝的线圈，在</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">0.4s</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">内穿过它的磁通从</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">0.02Wb</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">增加到</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">0.04Wb</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，线圈中的感应电动势为</span><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"1\" size=\"6\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。如果线圈的电阻是</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">10Ω</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，当它与一个电阻为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">990Ω</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">的电热器组成闭合回路时，通过电热器的电流为</span><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"2\" size=\"6\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></p></div>",
