          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">电动势为24V的电源，内阻为2Ω，若需保证电源输出的电流不超过5A，外电阻最小应是多少（<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'\" qml-space-size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>）</span></p><div class=\" qml-og\"><table class=\"qml-og\" style=\"width:100%\"><tr><td>A.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.8Ω</span></span></td><td>B.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.8Ω</span></span></td><td>C.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5.8Ω</span></span></td><td colspan=\"1\">D.&nbsp;<span class=\"qml-op\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2Ω</span></span></td></tr></table></div></div>",
          "answer": "<div class=\"qml-answer\"><span class=\"qml-an-sq\"><span class=\"qml-an qml-isop\">B</span></span></div>",
          "explanation": "<div class=\"qml-explanation\"><div class=\"qml-seg\" seg-name=\"详解\">【详解】<p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">要求电流I ≤ 5A，E = I(R + r)，24 = 5(R + 2)，解得R = 24/5 - 2 = 4.8Ω。</span></p></div></div>",
