          "source": "《电工技术基础与技能》综合练习（七）45分钟专题训练（原卷版+)",
          "year": 2024,
          "difficulty": 0.65,
          "stem": "<div class=\"qml-stem\"><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">某一闭合电路，电源的端电压与电流的变化图线如图所示，则电源的电动势是</span><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"1\" size=\"6\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">伏，电流的内阻是</span><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"2\" size=\"4\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">欧。若接某一负载要使电流输出最大功率，则负载的电阻值是</span><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"3\" size=\"5\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">瓦，此时电源的效率是</span><span class=\"qml-bk\" index=\"4\" size=\"7\" type=\"underline\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\" >　　　　　　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">%</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img  src=\"https://img.xkw.com/dksih/QBM/2024/12/5/3641755382104064/3644427209662464/STEM/90ec9402dec947f3bff86368ce708168.png\" width=\"196\" height=\"125\" /></p></div>",
          "answer": "<div class=\"qml-answer\"><span class=\"qml-an-sq\">① <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">4V</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;② <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&#xF057;</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;③ <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2W</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;④ <span class=\"qml-an\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">50%</span></span></span></div>",
          "explanation": "<div class=\"qml-explanation\"><div class=\"qml-seg\" seg-name=\"详解\">【详解】<p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">看图可知当</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">I=0</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">时，相当于电路断路，此时电压就等于电动势；书中</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">U-I</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">图的斜率为内阻</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">而此图是</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">I-U</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">图，故内阻应是斜率绝对值的倒数</span><math latex=\"$\\mathbf{P}=\\mathbf{I}^{\\mathbf{2}}\\mathbf{R}=\\frac{\\mathrm{E}^{2}}{\\mathrm{（}\\mathrm{R}+\\mathrm{r}\\mathrm{）}^{2}}\\mathrm{R}$\"><mrow><mstyle mathvariant=\"bold\" mathsize=\"normal\"><mi>P</mi></mstyle><mo>=</mo><msup><mstyle mathvariant=\"bold\" mathsize=\"normal\"><mi>I</mi></mstyle><mstyle mathvariant=\"bold\" mathsize=\"normal\"><mn>2</mn></mstyle></msup><mstyle mathvariant=\"bold\" mathsize=\"normal\"><mi>R</mi></mstyle><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mtext>E</mtext><mtext>2</mtext></msup></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">（</mi><mtext>R</mtext><mo>+</mo><mtext>r</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">）</mi><mtext>2</mtext></msup></mrow></mfrac><mtext>R</mtext></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，当</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R=r</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">时输出最大，此时</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">R=r=2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">Ω，由于内外阻相等，故效率为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></p></div></div>",
